{"tid":1515541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港自由之書］係時候揀封面啦","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:52:43.000Z","uid":208452,"like":30,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"70ef4c45e0906260a0692d2220762d875ad3340e","tid":1515541,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"又係我地自由之書團隊啊，我地之前都一直都搞緊物資野，好耐無更新過我地嘅進度啦，而家就同大家匯報一下<br />\n<br />\n多得各位義工嘅努力，我地己經整理曬全部大約1700份感想啦，同時間時序方面都己經大約寫左2月到8月8嘅內容啦，好快本書就會同到大家見面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">跟住就到今個Post嘅目的揀封面！</span><br />\n我地係義工嘅努力下，精選左兩個封面比人大家揀<br />\n正評：第一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiDhdOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiDhdOt.jpg&h=4decd46d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負評：第二張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SD7hYfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD7hYfe.jpg&h=0b35f226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">投票會系一星期後截止架，大家要快手啦</span><br />\n<br />\n另外補返我地嘅眾籌嘅Link：<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/hong-kong-revolution-documentary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhong-kong-revolution-documentary&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=8d362086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/hong-kong-revolution-documentary</a><br />\n我地其實離我地嘅目標仲好遠，大要幫幫手啊！<br />\n<br />\n另外我地附上我地比訪問：<br />\nApple daily<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190808/59907943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59907943&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=69d3d752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59907943&h=5315be19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190808/59907943</a><br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23019/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-23019/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23019%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-23019%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E4%25BB%2594&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=36edca14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23019/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-23019/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94</a><br />\n<br />\nSCMP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/society/article/3020848/supporters-find-ways-feed-mostly-young-hong-kong-extradition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F3020848%2Fsupporters-find-ways-feed-mostly-young-hong-kong-extradition&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=32f73f93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/society/article/3020848/supporters-find-ways-feed-mostly-young-hong-kong-extradition</a><br />\n<br />\n日本嘅日經就仲未出到"},{"pid":"cb890728610511f7268294a2eb2d8f63e0f405ec","tid":1515541,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d467334d1baea516a8296143b2d3d472e73b7a8","tid":1515541,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: larg